0by%20checking%20their%20individual%20X%20accounts%20is%20not%20an%20efficient%20use%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20project%2C%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20create%20a%20single%20webpage%20where%20I%20could%20view%20people's%20posts%20without%20needing%20to%20log%20in%20to%20a%20platform%20or%20visit%20individual%20feeds.%20To%20start%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20page%20to%20have%20three%20columns%2C%20each%20representing%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tesla%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-coding-job-market-software-engineer-students-openai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20for%20the%20columns%20to%20automatically%20update%20every%20time%20they%20post%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1b1ace5-10a6-4d17-9f6f-46a37205ec27%5C%22%3EFirst%20try%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222860%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20page%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68eff5325dbc4fd10daaea72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221374%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20failed%20webpage%20coding%20attempt.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Li%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20around%202%20p.m.%20local%20time%2C%20I%20started%20by%20telling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20had%20no%20coding%20experience%2C%20so%20we%20needed%20to%20start%20from%20the%20very%20basics.%20Then%2C%20I%20laid%20out%20the%20task%20in%20detail.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20created%20a%20brief%20plan%2C%20starting%20with%20downloading%20softw