3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Amazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20sat%20on%20the%20living%20room%20couch%2C%20filling%20out%20the%20campaign%20form%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20two%20high%20schoolers%20unprepared%20for%20the%20SAT.%20It%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20guesswork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20launched%20the%20campaign%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20August%20and%20almost%20immediately%20ran%20into%20our%20next%20obstacle.%20Remarkably%2C%20our%20campaign%20was%20suspended.%20Our%20product%20was%20deemed%20ineligible%20because%20%26quot%3Bcontent%20or%20products%20related%20to%20drug%20abuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222172%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20ads%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f118811c1f80efbec5b601%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22992%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Amazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDiscouraged%2C%20we%20didn't%20dig%20into%20the%20issue%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-September%2C%20we%20submitted%20a%20seller%20issue%20form%20to%20Amazon.%20Within%20a%20few%20days%2C%20our%20non-drug-related%20product%20was%20deemed%20eligible%20for%20advertising%20and%20the%20First%20Voyage%20officially%20set%20sail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20ads%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f118a7cc993f9955d05243%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20Amazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20can%20tell%20from%20the%20screengrab%20above%2C%20our%20initial%20ad%20campaign%20hasn't%20yielded%20much%20%E2%80%94%20or%20anything%2C%20for%20that%20matter.%20So%20far%2C%20we've%20traded%20%24373%20for%20121%20clicks%20that%20have%20resulted%20in%20zero%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20First%20Voyage%20taught%20us%20anything%