sh%20off%2C%20but%20it%20was%20persistent.%20Recurring%2C%20unexplained%20abdominal%20pain%20can%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-ovarian-cancer-when-to-see-a-doctor-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esymptom%20of%20ovarian%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20her%20doctor's%20appointment%2C%20she%20felt%20fine%20and%20went%20in%2C%20hoping%20to%20leave%20with%20nothing%20more%20serious%20than%20a%20recommendation%20for%20prenatal%20vitamins%2C%20since%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20planning%20to%20expand%20their%20family.%20But%20the%20stomach%20aches%20had%20been%20frequent%20enough%2C%20and%20severe%20enough%2C%20that%20she%20mentioned%20the%20discomfort%20to%20her%20doctor%2C%20prompting%20the%20ultrasound%20that%20ultimately%20found%20the%20tumor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis%20instead%2C%20Miller%20said%20not%20postponing%20her%20appointment%20or%20minimizing%20her%20symptoms%20may%20have%20saved%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227342c6bb-4ddb-44bc-ac9e-4fc23fcd069d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20loss%20is%20a%20reason%20to%20see%20a%20doctor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20had%20also%20experienced%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabrupt%20weight%20loss.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20related%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20her%20first%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20just%20losing%20the%20baby%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frise-in-cancer-among-young-people-under-age-50-charts-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%20with%20early-onset%20cancers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Miller%20had%20to%20make%20a%20quick%20decision%20about%20whether%20she%20might%20ever%20want%20more%20children%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eeven%20before%20she%20could%20do%20tests%20to%20find%20out%20how%20much%20the%20cancer%20may%20have%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'He%20said%2C%20'How%20much%20should%20I%20try%20to%20salvage%3F%20If%20I%20need%20to%20take%20everything%2C%20just%20understand%20what%20that%20means%20moving%20forward%2C'%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20ultimately%20decided%20to%20prioritize%20aggressive%20chemo%20and%20a%20surgery%20to%20remove%20her%20left%20ovary%2C%20but%20was%20later%20able%20to%20have%20a%20daughter%20naturally%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f801805-78cb-4e1f-a28a-e8ae37ae1d50%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBloating%20can%20be%20a%20subtle%20sign%20of%20cancer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%20said%20the%20stress%20of%20being%20a%20new%20mom%20made%20her%20almost%20miss%20another%20key%20sign%20of%20ovarian%20cancer%3A%20bloating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20swollen%20belly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-signs-of-ovarian-cancer-you-should-know-cancer-doctor-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euncomfortable%20feeling%20of%20fullness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20appearance%20of%20gaining%20weight%20(especially%20if%20the%20scale%20says%20otherwise)%20can%20all%20be%20indicators%20of%20several%20types%20of%20cancer%2C%20including%20ovarian%20cancer%2C%20colorectal%20cancer%2C%20or%20pancreatic%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20cancer%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%2C%20Miller%20said%20her%20mindset%20as%20a%20gymnast%20helped%20her%20face%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gymnast%20Shannon%20Miller%20competing%20on%20the%20balance%20beam%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68f1439ecc993f9955d0583d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22835%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiller%20was%20the%201996%20Olympic%20gold%20medalist%20on%20the%20balance%20beam%20and%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BMagnificent%20Seven%26quot%3B%20that%20brought%20the%20USA%20their%20first-ever%20team%20gold%20the%20same%20year.%3