OL%20in%20the%20first%20internet%20wave%2C%26quot%3B%20Draper%20said%20in%20a%20wide-ranging%20interview%20this%20week%2C%20where%20he%20discussed%20his%20views%20on%20investing%20in%20AI%20and%20his%20enthusiastic%20embrace%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20which%20includes%20creating%20multiple%20avatars%20of%20himself.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAOL%20and%20Netscape%20were%20the%20center%20of%20everything%2C%20and%20then%20came%20Yahoo%20and%20then%20Google.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20his%20doubts%2C%20Draper%20calls%20OpenAI%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%26quot%3B%20and%20says%20he%20regrets%20not%20investing%20in%20its%20early%20days.%20He%20was%20scared%20away%20by%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-reveals-fundraising-struggles-due-to-nonprofit-structure-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunusual%20non-profit%20structure%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20capped%20investment%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20had%20such%20a%20weird%20structure%20that%20I%20didn't%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Draper%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20probably%20should%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%2C%20even%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-culture-dotcom-housing-crypto-different-vibes-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20sounding%20alarm%20bells%20about%20an%20AI%20bubble.%20%3C%2Fa%3EDraper%20said%20there%20will%20indeed%20be%20a%20bubble%20bursting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hype%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt'll%20dip%2C%20then%20explode%20upward%20again%20and%20be%20bigger%20than%20anybody%20ever%20imagined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Draper%2C%20that's%20the%20nature%20of%20every%20bubble%3A%20Yes%2C%20there%20is%20hype%20and%20lots%20of%20losers%2C%20but%20there%20is%20also%20lots%20of%20money%20to%20be%20made%20because%20the%20underlying%20technology%20is%20still%20a%20game-changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20always%20feels%20like%20a%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20it%20gets%20real.%20The%20same%20people%20who%20were%20saying%2C%20'I'm%20not%20putting%20my%20credit%20card%20on%20that%20Amazon%20thing%2C'%20later%20couldn't%20live%20without%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22160c9ccb-cba6-4616-900a-b5c2fb605bce%5C%22%3EDraper%20has%20created%20AI%20avatars%20of%20himself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20said%20you%20can't%20be%20in%20two%20places%20at%20once%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraper%20is%20challenging%20that%20maxim%20after%20launching%20multiple%20AI%20avatars%20trained%20on%20years%20of%20his%20speeches%20and%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20having%20more%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Draper%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20some%20combination%20of%20my%20personality%20and%20all%20the%20interviews%20I've%20done%20and%20the%20books%20I've%20written.%20And%20every%20time%20I%20speak%20onstage%2C%20we've%20captured%20all%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Draper%20University%2C%20his%20accelerator%20program%20for%20entrepreneurs%2C%20students%20can%20interact%20with%20a%20virtual%20Draper.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20valuable%20to%20have%20me%20in%20a%20holographic%20form%20answering%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20spent%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20with%20it%20because%20it%20allows%20all%20of%20them%20to%20have%20better%20service.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20yet%20another%20avatar%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20founders%20in%20his%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20hotline%20for%20our%20entrepreneurs%20to%20answer%20questions%20that%20come%20up%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Draper%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20ask%20the%20AI%20twin%20first%2C%20and%20then%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20a%20satisfactory%20answer%2C%20they%20can%20always%20come%20to%20one%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20AI%20system%20that%20reviews%20startup%20pitch%20decks%20submitted%20to%20Draper%20Associates.%20Entrepreneurs%20upload%20their%20slides%2C%20and%20Draper's%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20twin%26quot%3B%20sends%20them%20feedback%20automatically.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20our%20own%20biases%2C%20but%20generally%2C%20the%20decks%20aren't%20all-encompassing%2C%20or%20they're%20too%20long%2C%20or%20they're%20too%20whatever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BOur%20AI%20can%20identify%20those%20issues%20and%20help%20the%20entrepreneur%20get%20better%20at%20presenting%20before%20they%20come%20and%20present%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraper%20has%20found%20that%20his%20avatars'%20biggest%20problem%20is%20that%20they%20are%20often%20addressing%20both%20sides%20of%20an%20issue%20instead%20of%20giving%20direct%2C%20definitive%20answers.%20He%20doesn't%20seem%20particularly%20worried%20about%20his%20AI%20avatars%20misrepresenting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20not%20saying%20the%20things%20I%20would%20say%2C%20I%20can%20go%20in%20there%20and%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20this%20is%20not%20accurate.%20We%20need%20to%20change%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20I'm%20working%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraper%20Associates%20also%20uses%20AI%20to%20identify%20five%20companies%20a%20week%20that%20the%20firm%20could%20invest%20in%20that%20might%20otherwise%20slip%20through%20the%20cracks%2C%20and%20he%20is%20training%20the%20model%20to%20constantly%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20at%20those%20companies%20and%20I%20give%20them%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20Draper%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20companies%20it%20is%20presenting%20to%20me%20is%20very%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20records%20all%20startup%20pitches%20and%20analyzes%20tones%20that%20can%20even%20identify%20potential%20deception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20evaluator%20that%20determines%20emotions%20and%20it%20detects%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20Draper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e11b21b-82a5-4066-b8e4-1bceb9115ea3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20AI%20replace%20venture%20capitalists%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20his%20embrace%20of%20AI%2C%20Draper%20does%20not%20think%20VCs%20will%20be%20replaced%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20an%20X-factor%20to%20every%20entrepreneur%20that%20AI%20can't%20really%20evaluate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20AI%20can%20look%20at%20their%20history%20and%20their%20competition%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20a%20while%20for%20AI%20to%20take%20the%20leap%20to%20backing%20an%20entrepreneur%20that's%20doing%20something%20AI's%20never%20seen%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraper%20says%20his%20curiosity%20cannot%20be%20replicated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ask%20the%20second%20question%20and%20the%20third%20question%20and%20the%20fourth%20question%20to%20try%20to%20dig%20in%20and%20figure%20out%20whether%20this%20is%20something%20really%20promising%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20still%20outperform%20any%20AI%20in%20investing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraper%20has%20amassed%20a%20fortune%20of%20%243.4%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%20Venture%20is%20often%20considered%20a%20young%20person's%20game%2C%20and%20at%2067%20years%20old%2C%20he%20could%20easily%20retire.%20Asked%20what%20keeps%20him%20going%2C%20he%20said%20he%20sees%20VC%20as%20a%20moral%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20good%20for%20the%20world%2C%20it's%20good%20for%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20people%20feel%20like%20they%20can%20start%20new%20businesses%20and%20they%20can%20change%20the%20old%20establishment%2C%20then%20you%20are%20going%20to%20make%20a%20better%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-draper-says-openai-is-todays-equivalent-of-aol-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C