r%20fun%2C%20Ali%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20hardest%20part%20about%20his%20job%20hunt%20has%20been%20this%20routine%20ghosting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20want%20me%2C%20I%20don't%20meet%20your%20criteria%2C%20at%20least%20have%20the%20courtesy%20to%20tell%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ali%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20of%20all%20ages%20get%20ghosted%2C%20but%20the%20silence%20can%20feel%20deafening%20for%20Gen%20X%20job%20seekers%20like%20Ali.%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20seven%20Gen%20Xers%20about%20being%20ignored%20by%20employers%20and%20how%20it's%20shaped%20their%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baf937e9-1c95-41be-81fc-bcbcb7c11b59%5C%22%3EAn%20unfamiliar%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYounger%20job%20seekers%20who%20have%20grown%20up%20in%20the%20digital%20era%20may%20not%20remember%20a%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-tell-youre-applying-to-ghost-job-not-hiring-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhere%20ghosting%20wasn't%20common%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20on%20dating%20apps%20or%20job%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20December%202024%20report%20from%20hiring%20software%20platform%20Greenhouse%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenhouse.com%2Fblog%2Fgreenhouse-2024-state-of-job-hunting-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E61%25%20of%20job%20seekers%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20ghosted%20after%20an%20interview%2C%20up%209%25%20from%20earlier%20that%20year.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOne%20reason%20ghosting%20has%20become%20more%20prevalent%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20is%20that%20employers%20are%20inundated%20with%20applications%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20tough%20job%20market%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplying-for-jobs-easy-hard-to-stand-out-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eease%20of%20mass%20applying%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busi