s%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EQuant%20investors%20speaking%20at%20a%20London%20conference%20this%20week%20said%20AI%20is%20more%20about%20the%20end%20user%20than%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20executives%20came%20from%20hedge%20funds%20and%20asset%20management%20arms%20from%20banks%20like%20Morgan%20Stanley%20and%20UBS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20quant%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20said%20AI%20has%20helped%20marketers%20sell%20computer-run%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20the%20latest%20edge%20in%20quant%20finance%2C%20which%20relies%20on%20math%20whizzes%20to%20drive%20computer-driven%20funds%3F%20Humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20ironic%20twist%2C%20the%20people%20behind%20quant%20funds%20are%20using%20some%20of%20the%20same%20language%20human-run%20stockpickers%20and%20investors%20have%20used%20for%20decades%20to%20defend%20their%20style%20against%20computer-run%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHuman%20creativity%26quot%3B%20is%20what%20will%20get%20quants%20ahead%2C%20said%20Amadeo%20Alentorn%2C%20head%20of%20systematic%20equities%20at%20Jupiter%20Asset%20Management%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20might%20be%20%26quot%3Btoo%20much%20hype%26quot%3B%20for%20what%20generative%20AI%20can%20do%20for%20investment%20management%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20advances%20from%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20have%20allowed%20quants%20to%20speed%20up%20their%20processes%20and%20work%20on%20more%20complex%20projects%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20not%20yet%20to%20the%20point%20where%20firms%20can%20turn%20their%20systematic%20funds%20over%20completely%20to%20the%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20far%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20generative%20AI%20is%20the%20end%20user%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Timothee%20Consigny%2C%20CTO%20of%20H2O%20Asset%20Management%2C%20a%20Paris-based%20macro%20manager.%20Consigny%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20London%20conference%20for%20the%20industry%2C%20called%20Quant%20Strats%2C%20compared%20the%20technology%20to%20driving%20a%20car%3B%20everyone%20now%20has%20access%20to%20F1-fast%20cars%20thanks%20to%20generative%20AI%2C%20but%20not%20everyone%20is%20able%20to%20drive%20them%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20on%20its%20own%2C%20AI%20is%20not%20going%20to%20help%20win%20the%20%26quot%3Balpha%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Matthias%20Uhl%2C%20head%20of%20analytics%20and%20quant%20solutions%20at%20UBS%20Asset%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20other%20than%20Citadel%20founder%20Ken%20Griffin%20agrees%20with%20the%20assessment%2C%20saying%20at%20Wednesday's%20Robin%20Hood%20conference%20in%20New%20York%20that%20generative%20AI%20%26quot%3Bfalls%20short%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20market-beating%20ideas%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fdfaeb3-0eb3-4f8f-8867-db6d18ce0b55%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20timesaver%20and%20marketing%20tool%2C%20but%20not%20a%20revolution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack-office%20grunts%20and%20marketing%20teams%20might%20be%20the%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20technology%20so%20far.%20Alentorn%20said%20the%20explosion%20of%20the%20technology%20has%20%26quot%3Bhelped%20selling%20our%20funds%26quot%3B%20because%20investors%20are%20more%20comfortable%20with%20things%20being%20run%20by%20a%20computer%20now.%20Uhl%20meanwhile%20said%20it's%20mostly%20doing%20%26quot%3Bmundane%26quot%3B%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20aligns%20with%20what%20funds%20told%20the%20Alternative%20Investment%20Management%20Association%20last%20year%20in%20a%20survey.%20While%20firms%20were%20using%20AI%2C%20the%20primary%20use%20cases%20were%20for%20%26quot%3Btime%20savings%20on%20administrative%20tasks%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcontent%20generation%26quot%3B%20for%20investor%20relations%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20to%20say%20quants%20dislike%20the%20technology.%20Stephan%20Kessler%2C%20who%20heads%20quantitative%20investment%20research%20for%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20allows%20us%20to%20run%20more%20systematic%20strategies%20in%20areas%20we%20haven't%20done%20before.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20AI%20combing%20bond%20prospectuses%20for%20crucial%20info%2C%20a%20task%20that%20used%20to%20take%20a%20person%20days%20is%20now%20done%20in%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20us%20to%20code%20more%20complex%20things%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Kessler%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20large%20language%20models%20are%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20a%20blank%20page%20and%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20funds%20what%20is%20important%20and%20what%20isn't.%20The%20software%20itself%20is%20not%20that%20valuable%3B%20as%20David%20Shelton%2C%20global%20head%20of%20FICC%20electronic%20trading%20and%20FX%20quantitative%20strategies%20group%20for%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20pointed%20out%2C%20AI%20companies%20are%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20away%20the%20code.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20what%20you%20feed%20the%20model%20is%20more%20important%20than%20what%20it%20was%20trained%20on%2C%20said%20Haoxue%20Wang%2C%20quant%20at%20Izzy%20Englander's%20Millennium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20language%20model%20can't%20read%20your%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20edge%20still%20lies%20with%20people%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquants-investing-ai-hype-grunt-work-marketing-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1760689741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62ffa584f1df7e0018eb53f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquants-investing-ai-hype-grunt-work-marketing-2025-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20technology%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20the%20end%20user%2C%20many%20quant%20investors%20said%20this%20week%20at%20a%20Lon