y%20that%20companies%20investing%20in%20AI%20may%20see%20a%20correction%20in%20the%20industry%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20certainly%20got%20some%20pretty%20prominent%20features%20of%20what%20looks%20like%20a%20bubble%2C%26quot%3B%20Clegg%2C%20Meta's%20former%20president%20of%20global%20affairs%2C%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClegg%2C%2058%2C%20was%20the%20UK's%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20from%202010%20to%202015.%20After%20leaving%20politics%2C%20he%20joined%20Meta%20in%202018%20as%20its%20vice%20president%20for%20global%20affairs%20and%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Meta%20promoted%20Clegg%20to%20president%20of%20global%20affairs.%20He%20left%20the%20company%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClegg%20told%20CNBC%20the%20race%20among%20companies%20to%20dominate%20in%20AI%20has%20resulted%20in%20%26quot%3Bunbelievable%2C%20crazy%20valuations%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20just%20an%20absolute%20sort%20of%20spasm%20of%20almost%20daily%2C%20hourly%2C%20dealmaking.%20Of%20course%2C%20you%20have%20got%20to%20kind%20of%20think%2C%20'Oh%20wow%2C%20this%20could%20be%20headed%20for%20a%20correction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Clegg%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClegg%20said%20in%20his%20interview%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20chance%20of%20a%20correction%20is%20pretty%20high%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20large%20amounts%20of%20capital%20needed%20for%20AI%20and%20its%20technical%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20investing%20billions%20into%20building%20data%20centers%20will%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Bprove%20that%20they%20have%20got%20a%20sustainable%20business%20model%20to%20recoup%20that%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Clegg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClegg%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20limits%20to%20that%20probabilistic%20AI%20technology%26quot%3B%20could%20make%20it%20